# Scoped for the tester-unified build (docker build -f tester-unified/Dockerfile .
# from the repo root). Whitelist ONLY the Python projects it COPYs, so the build
# context stays tiny — everything else (.git, .worktrees, logs, other stacks) is
# excluded. NOTE: this whitelist means a repo-root `docker build` sees only these
# four dirs; other stacks build from their own subdirectory contexts, not here.
*
!ciu
!cmru
!topos
!nyxloom

# Drop heavy/generated content within the whitelisted projects.
**/.git
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.hypothesis
**/.mypy_cache
**/node_modules
**/.worktrees
